hands_on_practices.solution:
流由 $\phi_t(\vec p)=M_t\vec p$ 给出，其中
$$M_t = \begin{pmatrix} 1+\alpha t  -\beta t \\ \frac{\alpha^2}{\beta} t  1-\alpha t \end{pmatrix}.$$
1. 生成向量场为
$$\vec V(\vec p)=\left.\frac{d}{dt}\phi_t(\vec p)\right|_{t=0}
=\left.\frac{dM_t}{dt}\right|_{t=0}\vec p.$$
2. 对 $M_t$ 求导：
$$\frac{dM_t}{dt}
= \begin{pmatrix} \alpha  -\beta \\ \frac{\alpha^2}{\beta}  -\alpha \end{pmatrix}
\quad\Longrightarrow\quad
\left.\frac{dM_t}{dt}\right|_{t=0}
=A=\begin{pmatrix} \alpha  -\beta \\ \frac{\alpha^2}{\beta}  -\alpha \end{pmatrix}.$$
3. 在 $\vec p=(\beta,\alpha)$ 处求值：
$$\vec V(\beta,\alpha)
=A \begin{pmatrix} \beta \\ \alpha \end{pmatrix}
=\begin{pmatrix} \alpha\beta - \beta\alpha \\ \frac{\alpha^2}{\beta}\beta - \alpha^2 \end{pmatrix}
=\begin{pmatrix} 0 \\ 0 \end{pmatrix}.$$
4. 因此，模为
$$|\vec V(\beta,\alpha)|=0.$$
